{"tid":949593,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"中國留美賓州大學生下毒害黑人室友","createTime":"2018-12-21T02:14:19.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-21T13:26:55.000Z","uid":184679,"like":18,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"ce732211b6fffdc7ff1ad3b11d58c33a37c77188","tid":949593,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-21T02:14:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20181221/640_2cb263d1b557980d0b0606f22469d1c4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20181221%2F640_2cb263d1b557980d0b0606f22469d1c4.jpg&h=b4177da2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n楊姓中國留學生涉嫌毒害室友遭警方法辦。<a href=\"http://翻攝newsweek.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F%E7%BF%BB%E6%94%9Dnewsweek.com&d=DcGHbNw%2B4eT%2BJYIid6iYFmi1w7%2FDyS2Kz%2BsYtkalU0Y%3D&h=cd55cb97\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">翻攝newsweek.com</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n美國一名中國留學生昨日向警方自首，坦承自己在非裔室友的飲料和食物裡摻入有毒化學物。該名男子犯案動機不明，但他曾在室友座位上刻著種族歧視字眼，已被警方以「種族威脅罪」法辦。<br />\n <br />\n22歲的楊宇凱（Yukai Yang，音譯）原是賓州理海大學的國際交換生，主攻化學。他今年5月因涉嫌恐嚇非裔室友、22歲羅亞爾（Juwan Royal）而遭警方調查送辦。據悉，楊宇凱曾在羅亞爾書桌刻上「黑鬼」字樣，並進行一系列破壞舉動。但警方同時也秘密調查，羅亞爾今年出現的神祕中毒現象是否與楊男有關。<br />\n <br />\n羅亞爾向警方表示，他2月時喝下房間內的一瓶水後喉嚨出現灼熱感，3月起更是莫名出現暈眩、嘔吐、不自主顫抖等現象，就醫後醫師為其抽血發現他血液中出現化學物「鉈」（thallium）。<br />\n <br />\n眼見行跡就要敗露，楊宇凱昨日向警方自首他就是下毒兇手。但他自稱當初購入「鉈」是為了考試成績太差而自殘。警方表示，楊宇凱涉嫌在羅亞爾放在冰箱內的食物中摻入無色無味的「鉈」，慢慢毒害他。而羅亞爾得知害他的是楊男時感到非常驚訝，因為他一直以為兩人的室友關係還算良好。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.appledaily.com/new/realtime/20181221/1487348/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fnew%2Frealtime%2F20181221%2F1487348%2F&d=DcGHbNw%2B4eT%2BJYIid6iYFmi1w7%2FDyS2Kz%2BsYtkalU0Y%3D&h=7af4e973\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fnew%2Frealtime%2F20181221%2F1487348%2F&h=9c7086e4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://tw.appledaily.com/new/realtime/20181221/1487348/</a>"},{"pid":"2a841c978b1c3d53ec800cf4425edf68f316a151","tid":949593,"uid":61660,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-21T02:16:03.000Z","msg":"個標題應該點斷句"},{"pid":"f295c48d88fb098f135727e4b4b2f36c50e32dbb","tid":949593,"uid":77196,"like":4,"dislike":2,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-21T02:17:02.000Z","msg":"第一眼睇咗做大學生賓州下毒<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"97fb55c64351ba72b2ae6eca51fb54b364cc50bf","tid":949593,"uid":107364,"like":7,"dislike":3,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-21T02:17:15.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f3aa90887fbdab0c7d7d7a3852af00078649067c","tid":949593,"uid":122134,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"quote":{"pid":"2a841c978b1c3d53ec800cf4425edf68f316a151","tid":949593,"uid":61660,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-21T02:16:03.000Z","msg":"個標題應該點斷句"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-21T02:26:28.000Z","msg":"中國留美,賓州大,學生下毒,害黑人室友"},{"pid":"83a126fe7b02c9c103b95f04f18339be156eaa9c","tid":949593,"uid":90269,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-21T02:28:35.000Z","msg":"賓州厲害大學"},{"pid":"541f433c54d93cc70091aa51db2ee65536512907","tid":949593,"uid":71508,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-21T02:51:58.000Z","msg":"@48"},{"pid":"474efd633ebc9d5600c7bb6a98c3a4b27fedbc0d","tid":949593,"uid":134381,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-21T02:53:26.000Z","msg":"而羅亞爾得知害他的是楊男時感到非常驚訝，因為他一直以為兩人的室友關係還算良好<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b926090559786094ac2801f470acd9b3c6c5ad1a","tid":949593,"uid":59001,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-21T03:11:34.000Z","msg":"中國留 美賓州大學生 下毒害 黑人室友"},{"pid":"385908f5747d80d74fa19037955f02663b9a9c6e","tid":949593,"uid":24140,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-21T03:19:21.000Z","msg":"中國 留美賓州 大學生 下毒害 黑人室友"},{"pid":"4edf97589198cc5e639e230e4b36974088fb1a29","tid":949593,"uid":41974,"like":1,"dislike":2,"